name: NBDY Julia
description:
Julia is the second in my NBDY series for anyone who wants a consistent character for their renders.

Julia is a Nobody, her unique look is a reflection of their individuality and originality, rather than an attempt to mimic someone else. The character's physical traits combined to create a look that is entirely their own, with no clear inspiration from any one person.

Julia has light skin, thick eyebrows, blue/grey eyes, and brown/red brown hair but will gladly try out other colors and styles.

To use this embedding with the Automatic1111 web UI, save the downloaded file to /embeddings/nbdy-julia-sd15.pt, and then include the trigger word nbdy-julia-sd15 in your prompt.

Inspired by Zovya's Nobody series. Be sure to check out other contributions to the Nobody tag.

If you like my work, please consider buying me a coffee to show your appreciation.

modelVersions.name: SD 1.5
modelVersions.description:
Tested with many models including photorealistic and anime, should be compatible with almost any SD 1.5 based model.

May have a tendency to create NSFW images depending on the model used.
